PIXON TECHNOLOGI said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 19.24% to NT$85,485,000 from NT$105,847,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             85,485          105,847    
YOY%             -19.24%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            337,787          362,897    
YOY%              -6.92% 
=================================================================
 